<plot>This is a promotional short for the feature film _Fame (1980)_ (qv). It tells the story of several students at the School for the Performing Arts in New York City. At this high school, students study dance and singing, and play musical instruments in addition to the standard subjects. Director 'Alan Parker (II)' (qv) explains his vision of the film, and several of the young performers are interviewed about the characters they portray.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?410592</url></doc>
